{"tid":836615,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（又嚟！）灣仔發展二期沉降最多101毫米","createTime":"2018-09-25T19:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T07:12:09.000Z","uid":79382,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e8d7dbc2dff1071e4a9d52813b8971fa3dafe980","tid":836615,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:36:41.000Z","msg":"明報頭條搶先睇<br />\n<br />\n【偵查報道】近期多項鐵路工程接連被揭沉降超標，由土木工程拓展署負責的「灣仔發展計劃第二期」，原來亦有沉降問題，是首次有政府工務工程涉及的沉降數據曝光。本報取得文件顯示，在2015至16年工程展開期間，灣仔北會展中心附近多個沉降監測點已錄得超出25毫米「沉降指標」，最嚴重的沉降點達101毫米&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/033632_03e809398ca626e79fd69a199e5ba8b0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F033632_03e809398ca626e79fd69a199e5ba8b0.png&h=dd94a215&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d38df6fcef3ef321da16ac3469aa122edac9e7d8","tid":836615,"uid":51620,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:39:01.000Z","msg":"隻龜要游出大海<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f648d4fba99d7cf625880d25a753d4b9a1bd86c","tid":836615,"uid":79382,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d38df6fcef3ef321da16ac3469aa122edac9e7d8","tid":836615,"uid":51620,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:39:01.000Z","msg":"隻龜要游出大海<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:40:17.000Z","msg":"要搵龜蛋喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7287862b8bad5adb9919d1573fd592ac921b5113","tid":836615,"uid":102609,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:44:18.000Z","msg":"仲講毫米？<br />\n都已經成10cm啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04363a9230cd8532ab06fefe46a7a444e2fff08e","tid":836615,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB